text: Kyzyrbak () is a rural locality (a village) in Salavatsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Maloyaz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Kyzyrbak
